5 brand new high quality strata units well situated at Monaro Business Park in Hume. Monaro Business Park is approximately 10 kilometres south east of the Canberra CBD and provides easy access to major arterial roads.

The development comprises tilt slab construction with high clearance, mezzanine office space, allocated car parks and high roller door access. The development has been cleverly designed for semi trailer access (providing a turning circle) and air conditioned mezzanine with energy efficient double glazed windows. The lighting is censored to save on electricity. High bay lighting has been included in each unit along with a clear roof sheet to allow extra natural light. Amenities include disabled toilets, shower and kitchens. These units are suitable for many types of businesses.

Hume is an expanding industrial suburb located some 15km south of CanberraAAaAas CBD adjacent to the Monaro Highway. The property is located approximately half way down Sheppard Street which is the main thoroughfare through the estate.

62 Sheppard Street is a flat regular shaped block with frontage to Sheppard Street. Constructed on the block is a single storey metal clad industrial warehouse of steel frame, concrete slab flooring and metal deck roof.

The rear area is available for lease. The area comprises approx 470sqm of warehouse with amenities including shower, toilets and kitchenette. The warehouse also comprises 3 phase power supply, alarm system and clearance heights between 5.3m and 7.8m.

The warehouse is also serviced by an exclusive yard area measuring approx 1,000sqm with 2.4m high perimeter fencing and gated access to the front. There is also a triple interceptor installed on site for the use of a wash bay.
